  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个虚拟资产转账的完整流程图，涉及Alice和Bob两个用户，以及各自的VASP机构。起点是Bob想收款，终点是转账完成确认。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "Bob",
        "Originator VASP",
        "Beneficary VASP",
        "virtual asset transfer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以Bob是收款方，他的VASP是Beneficary VASP；Alice是付款方，对应的是Originator VASP。我先确认一下角色命名——Beneficary这里是不是应该拼成Beneficiary？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Beneficary VASP",
        "spelling"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，确实是Beneficiary，你改过来吧。另外流程上，Bob先向自己的VASP发起收款请求，然后VASP生成Travel Address给他。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bob",
        "Beneficiary VASP",
        "Travel Address"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Beneficary改成Beneficiary。那Bob拿到Travel Address之后，是通过什么方式给Alice？直接发过去吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Beneficiary VASP",
        "Travel Address",
        "Bob",
        "Alice"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Bob把Travel Address发给Alice，然后Alice再告诉自己的Originator VASP去执行转账。这里要注意，Alice到Originator VASP是实线箭头，表示正式指令。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bob",
        "Alice",
        "Originator VASP",
        "Travel Address"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。接下来是Originator VASP做KYC检查，然后发Transfer Inquiry给Beneficiary VASP，带上IVMS101数据和Callback地址。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Originator VASP",
        "KYC checks",
        "Transfer Inquiry",
        "IVMS101",
        "Callback",
        "Beneficiary VASP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "没错，Beneficiary VASP收到后也要做KYC检查，然后返回Inquiry Resolution。这里两个VASP之间的交互都是实线，但Bob给AliceTravel Address那步用虚线，因为是用户之间的非正式通信。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Beneficiary VASP",
        "KYC checks",
        "Inquiry Resolution",
